  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 100,
      "options": {
        "content": "### How To Read\n- **Search Throughput (5m Rate)**: 每秒搜索请求数，按模式、执行路径和状态拆分。\n- **Provider Latency P95**: provider 搜索阶段的 P95 耗时，优先看 `completed` 曲线。\n- **Stage Latency P95**: `provider_search / result_map / result_persist / response_build` 四段耗时。\n- **Result Count P95**: 单次搜索返回结果数量的 P95，可用于观察结果规模是否异常缩小。\n- **Quality Scores / Signal Ratios**: 用启发式分数和新鲜度/权威命中率评估搜索结果是否还在满足业务目标。\n- **Review Scores / Bad Cases**: 采样后的规则和 LLM 评审，用来识别线上结果质量漂移。\n- **Source Imports / Async Job Outcomes**: 看搜索结果是否真的被导入，以及异步链路是否在失败或积压。",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "How To Read",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "每秒搜索请求数，按搜索模式、执行路径和状态拆分。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "decimals": 2,
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "notebooklm:search_requests_total:rate5m",
          "legendFormat": "{{mode}} / {{execution}} / {{status}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Search Throughput (5m Rate)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "搜索 provider 的 P95 耗时，单位毫秒。",
